  "description": "Ion live logs — what is Ion doing right now?",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## What is Ion doing right now?\n\nThis dashboard shows live activity across all Ion surfaces. **Verdict row**: log volume and active extension count at a glance. **Evidence row**: volume by component over time. **Right now row**: context pressure per session, dispatches in flight, TTFT, and backpressure. **Drill-down**: live log tail and per-extension activity.\n\nUse this dashboard when Ion is running a long task and you want to watch it. The live log tail at the bottom auto-refreshes every 30s. Filter by component (engine, extension, desktop, ios) using LogQL in Explore for deeper drill-down.\n\n> **Right now panels empty?** The context-pressure, dispatch, TTFT, and backpressure gauges require the Phase-B engine rebuild. Queries are valid; data appears once that ships."
      },
      "datasource": null
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Log lines",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed",
            "fixedColor": "blue"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": []
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({component=~\".+\"}[$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A",
          "__ionClass": "accumulation"
        }
      ]
    },
